description: Come get yourself some greatly tasty grub from Giggy’s BBQ & Catering. These fine folks are grilling up a fantastically gigantic selection of BBQ & Cajun creations that are all simply amazing.Whether you’re stepping up to their truck or taking a taste of their food at some gig, you’re just gonna love every bite of their offerings. Come and try any of their Sandwiches (like their Original Slow-Smoked, Pulled Pork Sandwich, or the Fried Shrimp & Sausage Po’ Boy), Burgers, Hot Dogs, and comfort food sides, like French Fries, BBQ Beans, Coleslaw, and the Giggy's list goes on... For a dining experience that’s really quite gratifying, get over to Giggy’s quick.
name: Giggy's BBQ and Catering
